                            <comment id="17941420" author="garydgregory" created="Sun, 6 Apr 2025 22:00:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=scoba&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;scoba&quot;&gt;scoba&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank you for your report.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is now fixed in git master and snapshot builds in &lt;a href=&quot;https://repository.apache.org/content/repositories/snapshots/org/apache/commons/commons-configuration2/2.11.1-SNAPSHOT/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://repository.apache.org/content/repositories/snapshots/org/apache/commons/commons-configuration2/2.11.1-SNAPSHOT/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;WRT to &lt;tt&gt;CatalogResolver.baseDir&lt;/tt&gt;, the code in 2.10.1 used to refer to the &lt;tt&gt;&quot;user.dir&quot;&lt;/tt&gt; system property, so I believe the current code is correct. Or am I missing something?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17941422" author="scoba" created="Sun, 6 Apr 2025 22:50:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the prompt response! You are correct... I misread the code in &lt;tt&gt;CatalogResolver.baseDir&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
What is the cadence for publishing new releases? My own projects are configured to disallow publication with SNAPSHOT versions.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17941423" author="garydgregory" created="Sun, 6 Apr 2025 23:24:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is no fixed schedule but I&apos;ll put this component on my to do list for this week.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17941440" author="scoba" created="Mon, 7 Apr 2025 03:52:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you! The SNAPSHOT release works as expected.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17943382" author="scoba" created="Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:38:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ggregory&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ggregory&quot;&gt;ggregory&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do you have an estimate for when you might be able to publish a new release that contains this fix?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;br/&gt;
= Scott Babcock =&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
